      "side": 1,
      "message": "The language to use was something I\u0027d pondered--part of me wishes a library would stick to one language.  This initial effort was to see how messy things would get going down this path, but also to quickly cook up a way to generate some pre-built constants.json files [I don\u0027t have am arm handy, and almost all of CrOS only uses 32-bit apps on that arch] should things go down that path (TBD on whether it\u0027d be minijail or another location where these files would be stored, though minijail would be the most central and its linux-x86/ directory is already a step down this path).",
      "parentUuid": "d3501a13_aec99037",
